{"content":"<li class=\"n-box-item date-title\" data-end=\"1473652799\" data-start=\"1473566400\" data-txt=\"Sunday, December 22, 2019\">Sunday, September 11, 2016</li><li class=\"n-box-item sa-box-item\" data-id=\"3208071\" data-ts=\"1473647366\"><div class=\"media media-overflow-fix\"><div class=\"media-left\"><a class=\"box-ticker\" href=\"/symbol/\" target=\"_blank\"></a></div><div class=\"media-body\"><h4 class=\"media-heading\"><a href=\"/news/3208071-asia-tumbles-following-fridays-decline-in-states-u-s-futures-turn-lower\" sasource=\"on_the_move_news_fidelity\" target=\"_blank\">Asia tumbles following Friday&#39;s decline in the States; U.S. futures turn lower</a></h4><ul>\n<li>The Hang Seng's <font color=\"red\">2.5% decline</font> is leading Asia lower following a similarly-sized drop in the U.S. on Friday. The Nikkei is <font color=\"red\">down 1.75%</font> and Shanghai <font color=\"red\">1.45%</font>.</li>\n<li>U.S. stock index futures are <font color=\"red\">down 0.7%</font> in Sunday evening action.</li>\n<li>In commodities, gold is <font color=\"red\">down $5.20</font> per ounce to $1,329 and oil is <font color=\"red\">off $0.80</font> per barrel to $45.09.</li>\n<li>The big selloff in bonds late last week looks to have triggered the rout in stocks, and a check of 10-year Treasury prices finds no bounce yet, with the yield flat at 1.67%.</li>\n</ul><div class=\"tiny-share-widget\" data-id=\"3208071\" data-linked=\"Asia tumbles following Friday&#39;s decline in the States; U.S. futures turn lower\" data-tweet=\"Asia tumbles following Friday&#39;s decline in the States; U.S. futures turn lower https://seekingalpha.com/news/3208071-asia-tumbles-following-fridays-decline-in-states-u-s-futures-turn-lower?source=tweet\" data-url=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/3208071-asia-tumbles-following-fridays-decline-in-states-u-s-futures-turn-lower\"><div class=\"icon share-btn c-email\" title=\"Email a friend\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-twitter\" title=\"Share on Twitter\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-facebook\" title=\"Share on Facebook\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-linkedin\" title=\"Share on Linkedin\">&nbsp;</div></div><span class=\"mc_gray_separator\">|</span> 10:29 PM <span class='mc_gray_separator'>|</span> <span class='comments-n'><span class='comments-container '>13&nbsp;<span class='comments-number'>Comments</span></span></span></div></div></li>","count":1,"message":null,"success":true,"today":{"start":1576990800,"end":1577077199,"str":"Sunday, December 22, 2019"},"yesterday":{"start":1576904400,"end":1576990799}}